{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 27.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That had to be '43, autumn '43, before we came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew, but therefore, they were isolated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that they wouldn't [? speak. ?]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Fredy Hirsch somehow was caught with the children, and they said his punishment was that he had to go afterwards, in September, to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these children--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Illegal.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were some workers and doctors who volunteered to work with these children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, they were sent to the east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we know from the Sonderkommando that all these children and all the volunteers and doctors who--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Must be around 100, 200, to even more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this group--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, we don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most probably, they-- when they annihilated the ghetto, they had in mind to do something with the children, maybe for exchange.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I told you, the Red Cross, at that time, was interested in the ghetto, Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were afraid the German Red Cross, they will need a cover, also for the people who went to the east.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And therefore, most probably, we were kept, the Czech family camp, and maybe also our group of children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that's unknown.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
